DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       This  program  combines three raster map layers to form a composite RGB
       layer. For each layer, the corresponding  component  from  the  layer's
       color table is used (e.g. for the red layer, the red component is used,
       and so on). In general, the layers should use a gray-scale color table.



